title: 30 Min Pilates FULL BODY Workout | Tone, Strengthen, & Burn Calories 🔥
description:
This thirty minute full-body Pilates class will tone and strengthen your hamstrings, core, obliques, shoulders, arms, glutes, and more!  

We will focus on helping you build a solid foundation of overall health and fitness to leave you feeling strong and centered.  

The result will be that you will radiate an incredible glow from the inside out, enabling you to share your authentic and beautiful light with the world around you. 

After the practice, check out the Free Blissful Body Bootcamp: https://free.bohobeautiful.life/fittoday & jumpstart your fitness routine! 🔥

Instructor - Juliana Spicoluk
Location: - Barbados
